  $}

  ${
    $d x y A $.  $d x y B $.
    $( The class union of the union of two classes.  Theorem 8.3 of
       [Quine] p. 53. $)
    uniun $p |- U. ( A u. B ) = ( U. A u. U. B ) $=
      ( vx vy cun cuni wel cv wcel wa wex wo 19.43 elun bilan andi bitr biex
      eluni bi2or 3bitr4 cleqri ) CABEZFZAFZBFZEZCDGZDHZUCIZJZDKZCHZUEIZUMUFIZL
      ZUMUDIUMUGIUHUIAIZJZUHUIBIZJZLZDKURDKZUTDKZLULUPURUTDMUKVADUKUHUQUSLZJVAU
      JVDUHUIABNOUHUQUSPQRUNVBUOVCDUMASDUMBSTUADUMUCSUMUEUFNUAUB $.
      $([20-Aug-93]$)

    $( The class union of the intersection of two classes.  Exercise 4.12(n)
       of [Mendelson] p. 235. $)
    uniin $p |- U. ( A i^i B ) (_ ( U. A i^i U. B ) $=
      ( vx vy cin cuni wel cv wcel wa wex 19.40 eluni elin bilan anandi bitr
      biex bi2an 3imtr4 ssriv ) CABEZFZAFZBFZEZCDGZDHZAIZJZUGUHBIZJZJZDKZUJDKZU
      LDKZJZCHZUCIZURUFIZUJULDLUSUGUHUBIZJZDKUNDURUBMVBUMDVBUGUIUKJZJUMVAVCUGUH
      ABNOUGUIUKPQRQUTURUDIZURUEIZJUQURUDUENVDUOVEUPDURAMDURBMSQTUA $.
      $([4-Dec-03]$)
  $}

  ${
    $d x y A $.  $d x y B $.  $d x y C $.  $( ` x y ` are dummy. $)
    $( Subclass relationship for class union.  Theorem 61 of [Suppes] p. 39. $)
    uniss $p |- ( A (_ B -> U. A (_ U. B ) $=
      ( vx vy wss wel cv wcel wa wex cab cuni wi wal ssel imland 19.22dv
