  ${
    $d A x $.
    $( A class is a subclass of the power class of its union.  Exercise 6(b)
       of [Enderton] p. 38. $)
    pwuni $p |- A (_ P~ U. A $=
      ( vx cuni cpw cv wcel wss elssuni visset elpw sylibr ssriv ) BAACZDZBEZAF
